data.description: Welcome to this classic two-story gem in sought-after beechwood neighborhood. This home offers a formal living room, formal dining room with built-in shelving, a cozy den, complete with a wood-burning fireplace, exudes warmth and character. French doors open to a delightful fenced backyard making it the perfect spot to relax and entertain. The two-car garage, with ample space for storage. Recent upgrades, including a newer roof, updates to the downstairs bathroom, fresh flooring, and a stylish coat of fresh paint and the water heater was also replaced in 2021. Conveniently situated near military bases, shopping districts, diverse restaurants, and local attractions. Seller currently has a 2.25% VA loan which may be assumable by qualified purchaser. Your perfect home is right here! Call for your private showing TODAY!
